Package com.cs115.rex

Implementation of the ReX application created as a term project for CS 115: Mobile Application Development at Mills College in Spring 2019.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ResultsFragment.Listener
    Interface to facilitate a click listener between the top-level activity MainActivity and the activities that it calls.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllergyInfoFragment
    Fragment attached to ProfileActivity which shows - and allows user to edit - their dog's allergies.
    DetailActivity
    Detail-level activity that allows users to view food detail pages.
    DetailFragment
    Fragment associated with DetailActivity that produces the detail page from the list of results.
    DogInfoFragment
    Fragment attached to ProfileActivity which shows - and allows user to edit - their dog's name, weight, and breed.
    MainActivity
    Top-level activity for the application, allowing the user to search and launching appropriate activities or fragments based on user interaction.
    MenuActivity
    Abstract menu class that displays a paw button menu item that links to ProfileActivity.
    MenuHomeActivity
    Abstract menu class that displays a paw button menu item that links to ProfileActivity and a dog house button menu item that links to MainActivity.
    ProfileActivity
    Top-level activity for the application's profile function.
    ResultsActivity
    Category-level activity that allows users to view the list of results.
    ResultsFragment
    List fragment associated with ResultsActivity that handles the list of search results.
    RexDatabaseHelper
    Helper class that provides database support methods for creation, data population and updates.
    RexDatabaseUtilities
    Helper class that provides database access utility methods.
    SearchFragment
    Fragment associated with the application's top-level activity MainActivity.
